@Environment(CLIENT) public static enum SimpleOption.DoubleSliderCallbacks extends Enum<SimpleOption.DoubleSliderCallbacks> implements SimpleOption.SliderCallbacks<Double>
A set of callbacks for a slider of values from 0.0 to 1.0 (both inclusive). There is only one instance of this callbacks.
